  $ cat > x.ml <<'EOF'
  > let x = {j| Hello, $()|j}
  > EOF
  $ melc -ppx melppx x.ml
  File "x.ml", line 1, characters 8-25:
  1 | let x = {j| Hello, $()|j}
              ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  Warning 108 [melange-uninterpreted-delimiters]: Uninterpreted delimiters j
  
